Bahrain Crown Prince to Meet U.K.’s Cameron Today, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-19T01:17:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-19/bahrain-crown-prince-to-meet-u-k-s-cameron-today-ft-reports.html
Bahrain’s Crown Prince Salman bin Hamad  Al Khalifa  is to meet U.K. Prime Minister  David Cameron 
today to discuss plans for reconciliation with the Shia majority
in Bahrain, the Financial Times said, citing unidentified
officials at Cameron’s office. Al Khalifa will also be meeting
policymakers and opinion formers in the U.K. and possibly in
 France  and the U.S., the FT said, citing people aware of the
matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 